	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107955119892318337">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.emacswiki.org/cgi-bin/community/ConnectingWikiEssay">CommunityWiki: ConnectingWikiEssay</a>.&nbsp; This is a great essay on Connecting Wikis that was <a href="http://collab.blueoxen.net/forums/cgi-bin/mesg.cgi?a=tools-yak&i=405881B9.1010404@fluxent.com">recommended by Bill Seitz</a>.&nbsp; This is apparently more by Lion Kimbro (wouldn't it be great if all Wiki were attributed somehow, even with annealing?).<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107955119892318337">Wednesday, March 17, 2004</a></span></div>
<br>
