	<a href="http://www.speakeasy.org/~lion/">Lion's Den - Lion Kimbro's Personal Web Site</a>.&nbsp; THis is a kind of Wiki Blog.  Lion Kimbro is here in Seattle.  His March 15 article is about Trans-Rational and it very interesting, as are the links and quotations from Michael Crichton.  There is also a February blog on <a href="http://speakeasy.org/~lion/#WikiProliferation">Wiki Proliferation</a> which is the reason that this Blog was referred to me, and others on CollabWiki by Bill Seitz.<br>
